Text:
The tracks are of a bearable quality (they are fine except for odd glitches that happen 2-3 times per song.)
Also, there are no track names/artist names etc. for any tracks.
Actually, the glitches happen quite frequently in some songs, making them quite difficult to enjoy. Anyone found a torrent without these glitches?

As others have said the glitches in this make it unbearable.

With regards to the actually tracks most of them are crap.  Disappointed with this volume tbh.
